  <li id="comment-43675" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/15474404078973540030" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Gail Gallagher</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2015/02/et-voila/#comment-43675"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2015-02-15T03:10:11-05:00">Sunday, February 15, 2015 at 3:10 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
