  <li id="comment-43676" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2015/02/et-voila/#comment-43676"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2015-02-15T07:30:39-05:00">Sunday, February 15, 2015 at 7:30 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love when kids personalities begin to really express themselves &#8211; such an adventure. </p>
<p>I&#39;ve been drinking homemade hot cocoa every morning around 10am for the last couple of weeks &#8211; half a cup of Valrhona powder, one bar of whatever artisanal 60% is on sale and 1/3 cup of coconut sugar (because coconut sugar!), whirled in the food processor.  I store it in a glass jar and just pour hot water over 2 tbls, because a hot water kettle is all I have patience for.  But I&#39;ll usually cool it down to drinking temp with a pour of coconut milk from the fridge.  </p>
    </div>

