    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Anonymous, Samie, and anyone else who wonders about the difference between natural and Dutch processed cocoa powders: check out <a href="http://www.davidlebovitz.com/2010/02/cocoa-powder-faq-dutch-process-v/" rel="nofollow">this explanation by David Lebovitz</a>.  In hot cocoa, you could use either type, but Matthew much prefers the flavor of natural cocoa, and so do I.</p>
    </div>

